{"tid":825372,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有錢人埋土拉把開房 窮撚勿入","createTime":"2018-09-17T13:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T09:04:25.000Z","uid":136467,"like":63,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"225afeb919fca015c112cc7c62116572e0f2e8bb","tid":825372,"uid":136467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:39:35.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今晚，唔返屋企訓了🚬。驚聽朝遲到，入拉把訓。<br />\n我地book了3間房。第一間喺24，最大嗰間，租的。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/213146_d0cad62873cd9079e4ef688c03e6cc02.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F213146_d0cad62873cd9079e4ef688c03e6cc02.png&h=047d5888&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有8個位，可以訓幾個人<br />\n另一間係左面倒數第二嗰間 坐6個人 細房<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/213256_3c193b54d5492f4a8b8b237b21927597.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F213256_3c193b54d5492f4a8b8b237b21927597.png&h=43e727ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n重有一間喺隔離，無圖<br />\n大約係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/213355_8f2a32800e942b5278ae60bb21730655.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F213355_8f2a32800e942b5278ae60bb21730655.png&h=304bee6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搞手會帶枕頭<br />\n自己敲門叫暗號&quot;金鐘M記&quot;<br />\n男仔: $1000位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女仔: model 靚女免費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n普通女仔: 唔俾去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n來吧靚女，識d俾得起1000蚊床位嘅有錢人吧。<br />\nPs 呢d開房無得賺，搞手只求打個和，大家開開心心訓返晚。"},{"pid":"ac454a9186dc6947ddeef6399b9ed89b2cf29e4f","tid":825372,"uid":199378,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:42:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"855fcb049ed8a28bae2a5bcc451fee29f4d81b52","tid":825372,"uid":196092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:43:36.000Z","msg":"金鐘McPoly<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ffee618d92fdd4099f71b4c6cbf58c7a407683","tid":825372,"uid":199211,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:47:24.000Z","msg":"埋土都有資格開po...."},{"pid":"cb1ea4affcbdae776433d02e18d4f190aeeea1f0","tid":825372,"uid":136467,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f1ffee618d92fdd4099f71b4c6cbf58c7a407683","tid":825372,"uid":199211,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:47:24.000Z","msg":"埋土都有資格開po...."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:49:37.000Z","msg":"對唔住<br />\n要識有錢人去吾城好啲<br />\n不過聽日要返學將就下ok?"},{"pid":"19da548d7795b9083ef9d0137efee21e261405b1","tid":825372,"uid":33631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f782645752f4ee9bcd45333516b4ae1fbbd4a91d","tid":825372,"uid":40804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:54:16.000Z","msg":"水浸喎ching"},{"pid":"f2f03f879e96f04c57542c627e1a686da225a048","tid":825372,"uid":136467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f782645752f4ee9bcd45333516b4ae1fbbd4a91d","tid":825372,"uid":40804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:54:16.000Z","msg":"水浸喎ching"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:55:43.000Z","msg":"有得玩埋水game<br />\n更加chill🚬"},{"pid":"c9ee427aaa4b62eb9fb363d6c7b5d9ad11f9797e","tid":825372,"uid":150720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:56:33.000Z","msg":"歡唔歡迎偽娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07060d6f39fc3188ae4976e224624e326f5603c1","tid":825372,"uid":136467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c9ee427aaa4b62eb9fb363d6c7b5d9ad11f9797e","tid":825372,"uid":150720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"